Work in progress.
---------------------

Frameworks and tools :
* Grails 2.0.1
* Groovy 1.8.6
* Java 7

Known compatible IDEs :
IntelliJ
Eclipse

Build this project from source :
* Clone the repository on your hard drive
* Install Grails http://grails.org/, put the binaries in your path

To build the plugin :
grails package-plugin

Roadmap
---------------------
* Github realtime repository view
* Compatibility with Spring Security to provide creation interface
* Integration with grails simple-blog plugin